lmodel= lm(Sales~TV,data=dataset)

#Plotting the Linear model
plot(dataset$TV, dataset$Sales,col="red",main="TV vs sales",xlab="TV",ylab="Sales")
abline(lmodel,col="blue")

prediction<-predict(lmodel)
residuals<-residuals(lmodel)
# Plotting prediction vs residuals 
plot(prediction,residuals,col="red")

attach(dataset)
par(mfrow=c(2,2))
plot(TV, Sales, col="green")
plot(TV,residuals,col="blue")
plot(Sales,residuals,col="magenta")
plot(prediction,residuals,col="red")

par(mfrow=c(2,2))
plot(lmodel)
